title: Wok to Walk
typeOfFood: Ovo, Chinese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Franchise Asian fast food eatery offer a 3-step menu with your choice of combination from different kind of noodles or rice, plus a fixed set of vegetables, optional extra ingredients (has tofu), plus sauce. Dish is cooked to order. Vegans need to specify no egg in the stir-fry or it will be added by default. Occupies the location of the now defunct Maoz Falafel.
